{
  "stem": "21788.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Erwin over here, who's always been a train fan, had to investigate the station, just like my father.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I didn't hear the train whistle blow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the train started to move, and I was outside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I was on the station platform.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the doors were closed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The train was going very slowly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I kept running towards the front of the train and finally, somebody pulled me in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Otherwise, maybe I would have still been left in Manchuria.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We went through Manchuria and came to the Port of Dalian.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "This is where we went to-- where a ship-- by truck-- to the Jewish Community Center.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we stayed in Dalian about two or three days to await the arrival of a ship that took us through the China Sea into Shanghai.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Again, all of our tickets, all of our fares were booked in advance.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We had first-class cabins on this small steamer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Well, what happened was, there were some Nazis on board that ship.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And they said, forget it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Nobody goes to first class.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Those Jews, they go down in the hold.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Like cattle pens is what they were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And that's where we had to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "The first meal, I remember, was served on us on metal dishes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "It was like slop.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And my father threw it into the cook's face.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And this was also the first time that I saw my mother and father hugging each other, breaking down, and crying.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I, I think that was the first indication what-- from things to come, of what China is like.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "This was a Chinese boat, and it was already pretty dirty.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "We, we, we could not stand the stench that went on down there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "We were only there overnight, but it was still pretty bad.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
